Matthi 01


1 Dayud amasung Abrahamgi macha nipa Jisu Khristagi miron lairik.


2 Abrahamna Isahak pok-i; aduga Isahakna Jakob pok-i; aduga Jakobna Jihuda amasung magi machin manaosingbu poki;


3 Aduga Jihudagi magi nupi Tamaragana Peres amasung Sarah pok-i; aduga Peresna Hesron pok-i; aduga Hesronna Ram pok-i;


4 Aduga Ramna Amminadab pok-i; 4 Aduga Ramna Amminadab pok-i; aduga Amminadabna Nahson pok-i; aduga Nahsonna Salmon pok-i;


5 Aduga Salmon-ga Rahabkana Boyes pok-i; aduga Boyesga Rutkana Obed poki; aduga Obedna Jisai pok-i.


6 Aduga Jisaina Dayud ningthou pok-i.

Aduga Uriyana louramba nupi adu Dayudna louduna Solomon pok-i.


7 Aduga Solomonna Rahaboyam pok-i; aduga Rahabboyamna Abiya pok-i; aduga Abiyana Asa pok-i;


8 Aduga Asana Jihosaphat pok-i; aduga Jihosaphatna Jouram pok-i; aduga Jouramna Usiya pok-i;


9 Aduga Usiyana Joutham pok-i; aduga Jouthamna Ahas pok-i; aduga Ahasna Hiskiya pok-i;


10 Aduga Hiskiyana Manasi pok-i; adugi Manasina Amon pok-i; aduga Amonna Jousiya pok-i;


11 Aduga Jousiyana Jekoniya amasung mahakki machin manaosing adubu Babilonda makhoibu pukhiba matam aduwaida pok-i.


12 Aduga makhoibu Babilonda pukhiba matung aduda Jekoniyana Saltiyel pok-i; aduga Saltiyelna Sarubhabel pok-i;


13 Aduga Sarubhabelna Abihud pok-i; aduga Abihudna Eliyakim pok-i; aduga Eliyakimna Asor pok-i;


14 Aduga Asorna sadok pok-i; aduga Sadokna Akhim pok-i; aduga Akhimna Elihud pok-i;


15 Aduga elihudna Eliyasar pok-i; aduga Eliyasarna Mathan pok-i; aduga Mathanna Jakob pok-i;


16 Aduga Jakobna Mariyamgi mapuroiba Joseph pok-i; Mariyamna Khrista koeba Jisubu pok-i.


17 Matou asum touna Abrahamdagi Dayud phaoba miron pumnamak adu taramari sui; aduga Dayudtagi Babilonda pukhiba phaoba miron taramari sui; adula Babilonda pukhibadagina Khrista phaoba miron taramari sui.


Jisu pokpa


18 Jisu Khrista asi matou asumna pokkhi. Ibungogi mama Mariyam asi Jousephta pibadi piraga luhongdringeida thawai asengbadagi mironle haina khangnarakle.


19 Amasung mahakki nipa Jousephsi dharmachenba mi oibana miyamgi mamangda phongdokningdraduna lonna thadokke haina ninglammi.


20 Touigumbasung mahakna matoiu asum khallingeida, yengu, prabhugi dudna mahakki mangda uhanbiduna hairei, he Dayudki macha Jouseph, nahakki nuri Mariyambu loba kiganu, maramdi mahakki nungda mironliba adu thawai asengbadagini.


21 Amahiksung mahakna macha nipa ama pokkani, amasung nahakna mahakki maming Jisu thon-gani, maramdi ibungona mahakki misingbu makhoigi paptagi kanbigani.


22 Prabhuina wa takthokpa mibu haihankhiba wa adu thungnanabagi damak pumnamak asi thoklare, maddi,


23 Yengi, leisabi asengbi aduna mironduna, macha nipa ama pokkani, amasung makhoina ibungogi maming Immanuyel kougani; madugi arthadi, eikhoiga leiminnaba iswar.


24 Amasung Jousephna tumbadagi hougattuna prabhugi dutna hairamba adugi matung inna mahakki nupibu loure.


25 Amahiksung mahakna macha nipa ama poktribaphaoba Jousephna mahakpu samnaramde; amasung mahakna ibungogi maming Jisu tholle.

EPHISA 5


1 Maram aduna nakhoina achanba machasinggumna iswargi matou loubasing oibiyu;


2 Aduga Khristana nakhoibu nungsibiraduna, iswargi maphamda nakhoigi damak ibungo masamakpu manam nungsiba oinaba katnaba pot amasung irapot oina pibikhibagumna; nakhoinasu nungsibada chatlu.


3 Touigumbasung nakhoigi narakta, asengbasinggi matik chabagumna, marumbi thamba amasung sengdaba pumnamakki nattraga karambagi maming phaoba pan-ganu;


4 Aduga amotpa machet amasung apangba wangang nattraga phagi jugai, pumnamak asi matik chade, adubu madugi mahutta thagatpa tousanu.


5 Maramdi asi nakhoina lepna khang-i, haibadi, marumbi thamba mi, nattraga sengdaba mi, nattraga lai murti latpa oiraba karamba mi kanaamatagisu Khristagi amasung iswargi leibakta phangpham ilei leite.


6 Mi kana amatana nakhoibu karisu nattaba wana minamdasanu; maramdi masigi maramna haiba indabagi machasinggi mathakta iswargi asaoba lak-i.


7 Maram aduna nakhoina makhoiga saruk phangminnabasing oiganu;


8 Maramdi mamangngeida nakhoidi amamba oirammi, adubu houjikti Prabhuda mangal oiri;


9 Prabhubu pelhanba karino munna khanduna, mangan-gi machasinggumna chatlu;


10 Maramdi mangan adugi maheidi aphaba, dharmachenba amasung achumba pumnamakta lei;


11 Aduga amambagi mahei yandaba thabak aduga mapang oiminnaganu, adubu madugi mahutta maral phonghallu;


12 Maramdi maldioina lonna touriba thabak adu haidokpa phaoba ikaibani.


13 Adubu phonghalliba pumnamak adu manganna phongdokhanbani, maramdi phongdokhalliba thabak khuding manganni.


14 Maram adugi damak hai, tumliba nang, yahouro, amasung asiba singgi maraktagi hinggatlo, aduga Khristana nathakta nganbigani.


15 Maram aduna nakhoina singdabagum oidaduna, asingbagum oiduna, karamna chatpa cheksinna yeng-u;


16 Achaba matam leijahou, maramdi matam phatte. 17 Maram asina nakhoina apangba oiganu, adubu prabhugi ningba karino khang-u.


18 Amasung yu ngaoganu; maduda wathok-lanthok lei; adubu thawaina thallu.


19 Amaga amaga dharma iseina, thagatpa iseina, amasung thawaigi oiba iseina ngang sak-u, aduga prabhuda nakhoi thawai yaona sak-u;


20 Maram pumnamakkidamak eikhoigi Prabhu Jisu Khristagi mingda ipa iswargi maphamda matam leiba khibikta thagatlu;


21 Khristabu kibana nakhoi nasen amana amagi makha ponnou.



Khristan imung manunggi mipal



22 Nupisa, Prabhugi makha ponbagumna, nakhoi nakhoimakki napuroibagi makha pollu.


23 Maramdi Khristanasu, ibungo masana hakchanggi kanbiba mapu, singlupki makok oibibagumna, mapuroi-bana nupigi makok oibani.


24 Touigum-basung singlupna Khristagi makha ponbagumna, nupisingnasu adugumduna maram pumnamakta makhoigi mapuroibasinggi makha ponsanu.


25 Mapuroibasa, Khristanasu singluppu nungsibiduna, ibungo masabu madugidamak pibikhibagumna nakhoigi nupisingbu nungsiyu;


26 Madudi, singluppu chusinba, kusinba, asinachingba karisu leitana adubu sengna amasung amakpa yaodana,


27 Luna-kena ibungona masamakta katchananaba isingna luthokpagi mapanna waheina sengdoktuna, ibungo na singluppu senghannanabani.


28 Adugumduna mapuroibasingnasu makhoigi masamakkumna makhoimakki nupisingbu nungsigadabani. Mahakmakki nupibu nungsiba mina mahak masabu nung-sibani;


29 Maramdi mi kana amatana mahakmakki masabu tukachaba leite, adubu mabudum yoktuna ngak senjei; Khristanasu singluppu adugumna toubi;


30 Maramdi eikhoi ibungogi hakchanggi kayatni.


31 Maram asina mina mapa mama thadoktuna magi nupida napsingadabani; amasung makhoi ani aduna hakchang amata oigadabani.


32 Athuppa wa asi arubani, adubu eina Khristagi amasung singlupki marida nganglibani.


33 Adum oinamakpu nakhoinasu mi khudingna masamakkumna mahakmakki nupibu asumna nungsisanu; aduga nupina mahakki mapuroibabu ikaikhumnasanu.

Philippiya 2


Amata oinaba amasung nolluknaba takpiba



1 Maram aduna Khristadagi karigumba insinbiba, nungsibagi karigumba themjinbiba, thawaigi karigumba tinnaba, karigumba nungsiheiba amasung chanbiba leirabadi,


2 Nakhoina chap mannaba nungsiba leiduna, pukning amata, thawai amata oiduna, pukning mannaduna, eigi haraoba mapung phahanbiyu.


3 Marannai tanbagi mapanna, nattraga napan toubagi mapanna amata touganu, adubu pukning nemthana masa masadagi atei ateina henna phabani singthanasanu;


4 Nakhoi mi khudingna magi magi marannai yengdaduna, atei ateisinggidasu yengsanu.



Jisugi nollukpa amasung masa kaithokchabagi pandam

n
5 Khrista Jisuda leiba pukning asi, nakhoidasu leisanu;


6 Ibungona iswargi maongda leirabasu, iswarga mannaba oiba adu chetna paigadaba oina singthanade;


7 Adubu minaigi maong louduna, mioibaga mannaba oiraktuna, ibungo masa mathantabu sangdokchare;


8 Aduga ibungobu sajatta mioibagumna ure, amasung ibungona siba phaoba, hoi, Krosta siba phaoba haiba illaktuna, ibungo masa mathanta nollukchare.


9 Maram adugidamak iswarnasu ibungobu wangna thanggatpiduna, ming khudinggi mathak oiba ming adu ibungoda pinabire;


10 Haibadi, swargada, prithibida, amasung prithibi makhada leibasinggi khuk-u khudingna Jisugi mingda nonjananabani,


11 Amasung mapa iswargi matik mangan-gi damak leiton khudingna, Jisu Khristana prabhuni haina haidoknanabani.



Lamchatna aran khubam matol lomba wa



12 Adunadi, eigi achanbasa, nakhoina matam leiba khibikta haiba inbagumna, eina leiba matamdata nattana hoijik eina leitabadasu amuk henna kina amasung tanik tanikna nakhoimakki aran khubam matol lomhallu;


13 Maramdi nakhoigi nungda ibungo mahakki apenbagidamak ningnanaba amasung thabak tounanaba, animak subiriba adu iswarnani.


14 Nakhoina apeiba amasung serannaba mi ron-gi marakta iswargi amakpa leitaba machasing, ayol aral leitaba amasung pukchel tingba oiraknanaba,


15 Murum murum sonba amasung khanjanaba yaodana thabak pumnamak toubiyu.


16 Miron asigi marakta hingbagi wa khut lanthoktuna, taibangpanda mangalgumna nakhoibu ui; asumna eina arembada chende nattraga arembada nomde haiba asi Khristagi numit aduda eigi chaothokchanaba maram oigani.


17 Hoi, aduga nakhoigi thajabagi bali amasung thougan mathakta eibu katthoklabadi, eina harao-i, aduga nakhoi pumnamakka loinna haraominnei;


18 Amasung matou aduga mannana nakhoisu haraobiyu, aduga eiga loinana haraominnabiyu.



Timothiya amasung Ipaphrodita



19 Touigumbasung nakhoigi maram khanglabada, einasu harao nungaiba oinanaba, eina nakhoida Timothiyabu thuna tharaknaba Prabhu Jisuda tarang tarang khangna ningjei.


20 Maramdi nakhoigi maram chumna cheksinbigadaba, magumna manana ningba eigi mi kana amata leite.


21 Maramdi makhoi pumnamakna makhoi makhoigi marannai adu thi, Jisu Khristagi adudi thide.


22 Touigumbasung makhoina mahakki aoiba adu khang-i, haibadi, machana mapabu thougan toubagumna, mahakna eiga loinana aphaba wapao thoina sandokpada thougan touminnare.


23 Maram aduna eingonda kari thoklagaba eina hek khangjabada, mahakpu eina tharaknaba tarang tarang khangna ning-i;


24 Adubu ei isasu thuna lakchagani haiba eina prabhuda thajei.


25 Touigumbasung eina eigi ichin inao, thabak suminnaba amasung lanmi oiminnaba, aduga nakhoigidi paopuba amasung eigi kannabada thougan toubida, Ipaphroditabu nakhoida tharakpa tangaiphadabani haina khalle;


26 Maramdi mahakna nakhoi pumnamakpu unaba khourangna pamjaduna, mathawai yamna warammi, maramdi mahak narammi haiba nakhoina tare;


27 Maramdi aoibamak mahak siningchit narammi adubu iswarna mabu chanbire; aduga mabuta nattana, eina awabagi mathakta awaba phangdananaba, eibusu chanbire.


28 Maram aduna nakhoina mahakpu amuk ubada haraonanaba, amasung eigi awaba khara hanthananaba, eina mahakpu henna pukning changna thare.


29 Maram aduna mahakpu taseng tasengba haraobaga loinana prabhuda lousinbiyu; aduga asigumba misingbu ikaikhumnabiyu;


30 Maramdi eingonlomda nakhoina thougan toubada awatpa adu samjinnanaba prabhugi thabakkidamak mahakna mathawai pammudaduna, siba tanna naksillami.

KOLOSIYASINGDA POLNA IBA LAIRIK


A-iba: Missionary Pol


Ibagi matam: A.D. 60-62


Wamachang: Khristadi pumnamakki mapuni.


Khristana pumnamakpu sembi. Mahakti thanggei sengpa Iswarmakni. Singlupki makoksi oiba amasung Iswarga taibang mioibaga tainahanbibasu mahakni haina taseng tasengna takli.


KOLOSIYA  1


Khurumjaba


1 Iswargi ningbiba mapanna Khrista Jisugi pakhonchatpa Polga eikhoigi ichin inao Timothiyagana,


2 Kolosiyada leiba Khristagi marida asengba amasung thajaba yaba ichin inaosingda eikhoigi ipa Iswardagi thoujal amasung ingthaba nakhoida leibisanu.



Iswarbu thagatpa amasung haijaba



3 Eikhoina nakhoigidamak matam leiba khibikta haijaduna, eikhoigi prabhu Jisu Khristagi mapa iswarda thagatchari;


4 Maramdi Khrista Jisuda nakhoigi thajaba amasung asengbasing pumnamakta nakhoigi nungsiba eikhoina tare;


5 Swargada nakhoigidamak thambikhraba tarang tarang khangna ningbagi maramnani; masigi maramda nakhoida leiriba aphaba wapaogi achumba adu tambibada nakhoina hanna tare;


6 Masi taibangpan pumnamaktasu mahei yanba amasung chaokhatpa oiba adugumna, nakhoina iswargi thoujal taraba amasung madu achumbada khanglaba numit adudagi nakhoidasu oibani


7 Masi eikhoiga minai oiminnaba achanba Ipaphradagi nakhoina tamlabagumbani; mahakti eikhoigi ihutta Khristagi thajaba yaba thougan touba mini;


8 Thawaigi mapanna nakhoigi nungsiba adu mahaknasu eikhoida phongdokpire.


9 Maram asigi damak eikhoina madu taba numittagi, nakhoina thawaigi oiba lousing amasung wakhal pumnamakta Ibungo mahakki ningba adu khangbana thanba oinanaba, eikhoinasu nakhoigi damak haijaba amasung nijaba tokte;


10 Nakhoina aphaba thabak khudingda mahei janduna, amasung iswarbu khangbagi mapanna chaokhattuna;


11 Haraobaga loinana khangheiba amasung kui na khangba pumnamak phaoba, ibungo mahakki matik mangangi panggan-gi matung inna panggal pumnamakna nakhoibu kalhanbiduna;


12 Aduga mangal aduda asengbasinggi phangpham adugi saruk phangminnanaba eikhoibu matik chaba oihanbiraba napagi maphamda nakhoina thagatchaduna, pumpen penba phaoba prabhugi matik chana chatpa oinanabani;


13 Ipa aduna eikhoibu amambagi panggandagi kanbiduna, ibungo mahakki nungsiba machanipagi leibak aduda eikhoibu hongdok pire;


14 Eikhoibu handokpiba, haibadi eikhoigi pap kokpibi adu macha nipa asida lei.



Khrista kanano amasung ibungogi thabak karino



15 Ibungodi uba ngamdaba iswargi murti, semkhraba pumnamaktagi hanna pokpa aduni;


16 Maramdi swargadasu prithibidasu leiba, uba pot, udaba pot, phambal makhei, angam athousing, mapusing, khutkan pangganbasing oira-basu, ibungodagi pumnamak semkhraba oire; pot pumnamak ibungogi mapanna amasung ibungogidamak semkhre;


17 Amasung ibungodi pot pumnamaktagi hanna lei, aduga ibungoda pot pumnamak ichang changi.


18 Amasung ibungodi hakchanggi, haibadi singlupki, makokni; ibungona pumnamakki marakta ihan hanba pham phangnanaba, ibungodi ahouba, asibasingdagi hanna pokpa oiri.


19 Maramdi ibungoda athanba pumnamak leinanaba,


20 Aduga ibungogi kroski igi mapanna ingthahanbiduna, prithibida oirabasu swargada oirabasu, leiba pot pumnamak ibungo mangonda ibungogi mapanna tainabinanaba, iswarna penbiba oire.


21 Amasung nakhoidi mamangngeida phattaba thabakki marakta mitop amasung nakhoigi pukningda yeknabasing oiramba adu,


22 Houjikti ibungo mahakki mangda nakhoibu sengna, amakpa leitana amasung paothokpa leitana katchananaba, ibungogi mioibagi hakchangda sibagi mapanna ibungona tainabire;


23 Nakhoina taraba, swargagi makhada leiba semkhraba pumnamakta sandokkhraba, Pol eina thougal touba mi oijarakkhiba, aphaba wapao adugi tarang tarang khangna ningba adudagi lengdaduna, nakhoina thajabada leitana chetna itattattana leirabadi, hairiba asi nakhoigi oigani.



Khristagi thabakta polgi saruk



24 Houjik eina nakhoigi maramgidamak eigi awa khangjabada haraojei, aduga singlup oiriba, ibungogi hakchanggi maramgidamak eigi isada Khristagi awa anang wat-houba adu eigi ithoudang hapchinjei;


25 Yug yugtagi amasung miron mirondagi lotlakliba athuppa iswargi wa adu suna sandoknaba, nakhoigidamak eingonda pikhraba iswargi asin arangba thabak adugi matung inna, eina singlup adugi maramda thougan touba oijarakle;


26 Adubu houjikti athuppa wa adu ibungo mahakki asengbasingda phongdokpire;


27 Makhoi asida iswarna atoppa jatsinggi marakta athuppa wa asigi matik mangan-gi ayamba adu karino khanghanningle, madudi matik mangangi tarang tarang khangna ningba, nakhoida leiba Khristaduni.


28 Eikhoina mi khuding-bu Khristada mapung phana katchananaba, lousing pumnamakna mi khudingbu waraktuna amasung mi khudingbu tambiduna, ibungo asigi pao eikhoina sandokchabani;


29 Asigidamak eigi nungda panggal thekna touriba ibungogi thabak adugi matung inna angam tan-duna, einasu nomjari.

I THESLONIKIYA 3


Timothiyabu tharakpa



1 Maram adugi damak amuk henna khangba ngamdrabada, Athinayada ithanta leihouba phei haina eikhoina ningle;


2 Aduga awa anang asina mi kana amatabu lenghanda nanaba, nakhoigi thajaba marida nakhoibu chethannaba amasung pangbinaba eikhoigi ichin inao amasung Khristagi aphaba wapaoda iswargi thougan touba Timothiyabu thare;


3 Maramdi awa anang asigi damak eikhoibu thamle haiba nakhoi nasana khangbani.


4 Maramdi eikhoina nakhoiga loinana leiringeida, eikhoina awa anang khanggadabani haiba hanna nakhoibu tambire; asumna thoksu thokle, aduga nakhoinasu khang-i.


5 Maram asigi damak einasu amuk henna khangba ngamdrabada, karigumba pambeina nakhoibu athemba mapuna themdokhiba yai, amasung eikhoigi nomjaba aremba oiba yai haiduna eina nakhoigi thajaba khangjananaba mahakpu thare.


6 Touigumbasung Timothiyana houjik nakhoidagi eikhoida laktuna, nakhoigi thajaba amasung nungsibagi haraoba pan, aduga eikhoinasu nakhoibu ujaning-bagumna nakhoina eikhoibu unanaba khourangduna matamleibakhibikta eikhoibu phajana ningsingihaiba eikhoida tamlare;


7 Maram asigi damak, ichin inaosa, nakhoigi maramda eikhoigi anangba amasung awaba pumnamakta nakhoigi thajaba mapanna eikhoibu themjinbire;


8 Maramdi nakhoina prabhuda chetna leplabadi, houjik eikhoi hing-i.


9 Maramdi eikhoina nakhoigi mai ujananaba amasung nakhoigi thajaba watpa adu changkhonhannanaba, ahing nungthil thoidok hendokna nonjaduna,


10 Eikhoigi iswargi mangda nakhoigi maramda eikhoina haraojaba maharao pumnamak adugi damak eikhoina iswargi maphamda karamna amuk henna thagatchaba ngamgadage?


11 Houjikti eikhoigi iswar amasung Ipa Ibungo mahakmakna aduga eikhoigi Prabhu Jisuna eikhoigi lambi nakhoi tanna chingbisanu;


12 Aduga eikhoinasu nakhoiromda nungsibagumna, nakhoi amana amada amasung mi pumnamaklomda nakhoigi nungsiba Prabhuna hengathan-biduna yamhahbisanu;


13 Asumna eikhoigi Prabhu Jisuna Ibungogi asengbasing pumnamakka loinana lenglakpada, eikhoigi ipa iswargi mangda ibungona pukning ayol aral leitana asengbada chethanbisanu.
